<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Onboarding Successful - Course Enrolment Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;
      } .logo { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px; } .logo img { max-width:
      235px; } h1 { color: #b7202f; } table { width: 100%; border-collapse:
      collapse; margin-top: 20px; } th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding:
      10px; text-align: left; } th { background-color: #f2f2f2; } .footer {
      margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img
          src="https://lms-kjsce.somaiya.edu/pluginfile.php/1/theme_essential/logo/1716970170/engg-logo.png"
          alt="KJ Somaiya College Of Engineering"
        />
      </div>
      <h1>Course Enrolment Confirmation</h1>
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>Your enrolment has been recorded successfully. Below is a summary of
        your enrolment:</p>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Course Name</th>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>Mode</th>
            <th>Hours</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {{#each courses}}
            <tr>
              <td>{{this.course_name}}</td>
              <td>{{this.type}}</td>
              <td>{{this.mode}}</td>
              <td>{{this.total_hours}}</td>
            </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes, please reach out to
        your departmental OET-OEHM coordinators.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>